Tales From The Crypt (5) SONGS ● (2021) This Exclusive Extended Play ( E.P. ) was released on all major streaming platforms. Some people still always ask how did this project come about well after things didn't work out as planned with @itsilovemusic @sonymusic @the_orchard_ i lost alot of momentum and I was again a independent artist 🎨  after that everyone kept asking what happened with you and Sony ??.. due to Rambo having a servere medical issue whatever what was on the table disappeared. So I had to think what was going to be my new approach, how can I position my self to continue my journey. One night I was watching scary movies and goosebumps appeared on my tv screen so I decided to watch it then BOOM!! it hit me to come up with a name that everyone is familiar with a name thats monetized so I got deeper in my thoughts and " Tales From The Crypt Keeper " was the next idea 💡  quickly I looked up some old episodes and I watched more than I expected so it hit me to reuse the title and that's what I did I got with a #Memphis producer and pitched him the idea and he started cooking 🍳. My management team didn't  approve of it because they only wanted me to release singles. I clearly understood but I felt this call was on me. Obviously I'm built for this but it was more like @tombrady on the field even tho #billbelichick  said run the play but the QB goes with his gut and run it his way.. FYI the coach isn't always right but if your wrong boy you're in trouble. So I decided to run my play with @p_eewee he did mention only big artists put out these projects and if you don't plan on pushing this for at 3 years don't waste my fckin time ... boy was he not easy to deal with but I agreed upon that and he okayed it.. so to work is where I went... ive collaborated with @dgb_offtheporch @whoishidef @yaadi_hardbody @nomoreheroespresents and now I'm looking at 1,834,143 Streams a few labels reach out I haven't accepted but I got the results I was looking for 📄 #spotify #music #youtube #applemusic #hiphop #newmusic #itunes #talesfromthecrypt #rap #podcast #artist #rapper #tidal #producer #deezer #spotifyplaylist #musician #explorepage #trap #beats #dj #youngjr
